parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Engine Failure Due to Oil Consumption
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the engine can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded, which can put the driver and passengers at risk of injury or death.

the check engine light comes on
the oil light flickers or comes on
the engine makes a loud noise
and the engine oil level drops rapidly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission and gear shifter problems can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or become stuck in gear, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The gear shifter may lock in place

causing the vehicle to lose power or stall.
